title: MEMORY.md session-privacy gate
---
AGENTS.md specifies that MEMORY.md must only be loaded in direct/private sessions — never group chats or multi-participant contexts. Currently prompt_builder injects all workspace files regardless of session type. Add a session_type field (private|group) to the agent turn context and conditionally exclude MEMORY.md (and other sensitive files) when session_type=group. Depends on per-message context injection (T002) for the session type signal.